{"tid":1550613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講左好多次左膠永遠唔係同路人 班智障成撚日話屌左膠就係分化割蓆 你鍾意比左膠累到比人斬比人拉你死你事 唔好累鳩其他手足","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T17:21:51.000Z","uid":252492,"like":94,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"02f785e3cb6531e6a16fc3d575272c438038b47b","tid":1550613,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8e0ba10704931ed8d7e71777d4f22ec635cdce14","tid":1550613,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67a4fd01ba6ce7f4db505f6882eb18fb9bb93f9e","tid":1550613,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f2e7d0cf47bc5847bef7dea766b78f7046cca5","tid":1550613,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea37daa0c3ee96997ba56a853af7d29d2fb33c06","tid":1550613,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:53:26.000Z","msg":"其實上次輸主因左膠⋯"},{"pid":"5d8262089247e72c438e36fc03668792a0eeacd8","tid":1550613,"uid":65439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一早講撚左<br />\n前幾日某個post既巴打仲屌返我轉頭問點解唔剩係拉走d左膠<br />\n 831勇武戀戰先搞到走唔甩 屌你老母 我想搵返條撚樣出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5155b9e1e3b289876a8897183d9927586d659d15","tid":1550613,"uid":8600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256fe2f26ceb4d45e84ef8101d9c810fd4b435ea","tid":1550613,"uid":132079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:57:33.000Z","msg":"剛剛tko 又一件"},{"pid":"7e18f723c594706ce9065685c1ee54665808faa4","tid":1550613,"uid":262997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"香港人新精神：打狗救人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550408</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫我推上去！"},{"pid":"fbee4b3776974eff2d25523645a559ecf799e897","tid":1550613,"uid":248131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02f785e3cb6531e6a16fc3d575272c